[l] Die neuen Terroristen: Schwarzfahrer."When we talk about criminal actors, a person about to commit a robbery on a Muni coach is typically not paying their fare," Cmdr. Mikail Ali said. "Fare evasion is the nexus by which we make those initial contacts [with criminals]."Fare-evasion enforcement is a way to catching more serious criminals, Ali said, "who in some cases possess firearms while on Muni coaches."Increased police presence is a deterrent to acts of terrorism, he said. "That's a good thing."In essence, terrorists could be more likely to be fare cheats.Also wenn das keine stringente, ueberzeugende Argumentation ist, dann weiss ich auch nicht.
